{"tid":1752711,"cid":5,"subCid":10,"title":"麥美娟歸咎政府累積民怨　梁耀忠稱市民關注警暴問題","createTime":"2019-11-24T23:11:53.000Z","updateTime":"2019-11-25T01:23:50.000Z","uid":130626,"like":2,"dislike":2,"uniUserReply":16,"replies":[{"pid":"513aecd18ccfc5dd5a0b27ff6601eca4741a7350","tid":1752711,"uid":130626,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-11-24T23:11:53.000Z","msg":"區議會選舉結果揭盅，多個建制派政黨受「重創」，其中民建聯兩名副主席張國鈞及周浩鼎都落敗；服務葵青區26年的工聯會麥美娟、做了兩屆區議員的「雙料議員」田北辰，均未能連任。麥美娟相信，今次落敗與政府累積民怨有關。<br />\n<br />\n至於民主派在區選成績亮麗，民主黨5名參選的立法會議員順利連任，街工梁耀忠、新盟主同盟范國威亦都成功擊敗對手。<br />\n<br />\n梁耀忠認為，選舉結果是市民給予政府明確訊息，警暴問題不能持續。<br />\n<img src=\"https://newsstatic.rthk.hk/images/mfile_1494254_1_L_20191125063134.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fnewsstatic.rthk.hk%2Fimages%2Fmfile_1494254_1_L_20191125063134.jpg&h=e95a1112&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<a href=\"https://news.rthk.hk/rthk/ch/component/k2/1494254-20191125.htm?spTabChangeable=0\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fnews.rthk.hk%2Frthk%2Fch%2Fcomponent%2Fk2%2F1494254-20191125.htm%3FspTabChangeable%3D0&d=N9koirI5nbtQ%2BujBUnukppMi8MJ45PejcSMOUziyDL0%3D&h=1e16b14b\" data-ef-url=\"https://embed.lih.kg/frame?u=https%3A%2F%2Fnews.rthk.hk%2Frthk%2Fch%2Fcomponent%2Fk2%2F1494254-20191125.htm%3FspTabChangeable%3D0&h=00ff20cb\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://news.rthk.hk/rthk/ch/component/k2/1494254-20191125.htm?spTabChangeable=0</a>"},{"pid":"7e01cc0d8efe5a7a225583a8653eb9bc4fb309b6","tid":1752711,"uid":263261,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-11-24T23:12:48.000Z","msg":"割了割了<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/hehe.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"063dd8e6f936963738dbb2692be9f225edecc6c4","tid":1752711,"uid":36178,"like":3,"dislike":2,"score":1,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-11-24T23:12:59.000Z","msg":"你收撚皮啦, 梁耀忠<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/norma